"Skull Fuct" song overview: Light Asylum are currently busy away in the studio where they are recording their debut album which is set for a release in May on Mexican Summer. To soften the wait, the duo had a video made for Skull Fuct (taken from their In Tension EP), which was shot and directed by Emilxa Xuryłowicz and Cezary Zacharewicz.
